title: #92Noon! Fleck/Leber/Birk/Talkers
description: Gophers coach PJ Fleck opens the show, followed by a Summertime parody and Farmer fodder to end the first hour. Ben Leber's weekly appearance and an impromptu Jonny Athletic hit get us to the final stretch, where the Birk Bit comes in studio!
